      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im still doing this. everything just feels so heavy lately. the lab results, the funding stuff... it feels like i've spent years building my whole life around a version of myself that just doesn't exist anymore. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to keep my head above water. i just want everything to stop. i just want some peace.",
